videos.description: John Fulkerson leads Tennessee with 24 points as they knock Arizona from the undefeated ranks.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Arizona Wildcats vs. Tennessee Volunteers: Full Highlights) 2021/12/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tennessee holds off comeback attempt, hands Arizona its first loss

videos.description: After leading No. 19 Tennessee to a 77-73 victory over No. 6 Arizona with 24 points and 10 rebounds, John Fulkerson praises the Vols' home crowd.
videos.headline: Fulkerson says fans energized UT in upset of Arizona
